original: Landegren, Per Bengt, kamrer, Göteborg, f. 1/11/08 i Eskilstuna av rev. B. L. o. Ebba Landahl. G. m. Barbro Necander. — Studrex. samt ekon. ex. v. handelshögsk. i Gbg. Tidigare anst. v. Eskilstuna Jernmanuf. A-B, Hans Helsen & Co. i Hamburg samt iLlektrokem. A-B i Bohus, numera kamrer h. Västsv. Mejeriernas Centralförb. i Gbg. Resor t. bl. a. Tys’kl. 27-28 o. 29.
translated: Landegren, Per Bengt, accountant, Gothenburg, born 1/11/08 in Eskilstuna to reverend B. L. and Ebba Landahl. Married to Barbro Necander. — Completed studies and received a degree in economics from the School of Business, Economics and Law in Gothenburg. Previously employed at Eskilstuna Jernmanuf. A-B, Hans Helsen & Co. in Hamburg, as well as at Elektrokem. A-B in Bohus. Currently employed as an accountant at Västsvenska Mejeriernas Centralförbund in Gothenburg. Has traveled to, among other places, Germany in 1927-1928 and 1929.
